overview.en: Dcoin Token (DT) is a Global Utility Token issued by ESPBC Foundation for Dcoin Exchange and its eco-system. DT holders have the privilige to participate in Dcoin community autonomy and ecological co-construction.
overview.zh: Dcoin Token (DT)为由ESPBC基金会发行的Dcoin Exchange全球通用积分。DT采用全球首个多币种混链共振发行的方式，旨在服务于社区共建，实现开放管理、持续发展的自由交易平台。
